Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.00,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}翻译：傻瓜三世 ZERO 逆火 校对：傻瓜三世\N\N后期：Misaki喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别废话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才不想来这种地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}闭嘴 要是想保住这家伙的命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就快把钱交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.80,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命 我还有宝贵的乌龟和土拨鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我只是个打零工的 您还是去找银行职员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在不是嬉闹的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们还在笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是嘲笑的话 小理多可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月 你这样才是最伤人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了 小理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铃 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那张脸是怎麽了 快拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好不容易见个面 第一句话就这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新年前一天的转播 老姐你要这样出镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:54.59,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肚子笑好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在探讨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有三宅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的朋友听说测试转播的事 就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三宅 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那件事后就联繫不上你 我们很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:17.97,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛 脚扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑对不起 之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…日向？
