Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本向新基地送出物资的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通过DROMLAN 也给我们送来了这些补充物资
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.88,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※DROMLAN\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}毛德皇后地航空网路项目，是由南极洲东部建立基地的11个国家签署的，借用两个考察站{\r}\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}（挪威特罗尔站、俄罗斯新拉扎列夫站）的长距离冰跑道，作为国际飞机中转站的合作交通协议。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的资材就算齐全了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要今年立刻搭建起观星天文台 还是天方夜谭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过只要有心坚持 花上几年时间估计…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们得去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少所有人都是这麽想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那是贵子断绝音信的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该怎麽办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老妈肯定把照片传遍SNS了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不也很好吗 这样还能宣传我们的转播呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…我的也麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贺年卡只写给店长一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才那几个朋友不用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 虽说是贺年卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也要等到船回到日本后才能送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那麽痛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是不是在紧张啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑也要去上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开什麽玩笑 开什麽玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开什麽玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开什麽玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以可以带我们参与海冰和地质的调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会准备摄影机的 你要想好怎麽报导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}探险探险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说要做报导的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不管你等一下情不情愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向 就是刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才只是测试 所以不算欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点 马上就要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年前就一起做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁叫贵子前辈什麽都想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 她到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑 你妈妈还来过这裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个拿来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这下面都是冰块 所以要用蒸汽热个洞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 我们去的应该是伦湾角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(830,650)\clip(726,610,936,660)}（Rundvågshetta）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这名字听起来就好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是个岩石裸露的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你找信惠 她可能愿意带你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡是海冰组
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地质组的信惠小姐听得到吗 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}联繫不上 圣诞之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大前年收到的石榴石…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾燥的岩石 和乾涸的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收不到邮件 冷淡的阿优
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在无法联络 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊 这温差好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别弄我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们看 好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极好壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从这个角度看很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天空在眼前流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道能不能看到极光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们在的这段时间 不会有夜晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有没有什麽烦心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}烦心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空气太乾燥 嘴唇都乾巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}护唇膏也冻得硬邦邦的 很难涂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的确很难受 感觉都要脱皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.79,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}户外队员请立刻回到基地中央区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是到有应急食品的建筑内避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全没改善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说报濑人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才有人问她会不会打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 她会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉很有趣 我也在她背后观摩了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人字旁加个五读作什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准备好的白板正好凑一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是准备好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个鸟好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「滚出去！」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就问她几句嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑本来就心胸狭隘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\an5\fs30\1c&H767876&\frx328\fry14\pos(998,114)\frz333.8}封锁名单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H7262CA&\frz333.5\frx328\fry2\pos(522,482)}删除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&HAD9981&\pos(450,618)\frz331\frx340\fry4}解除封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}门清混一色 双南风 宝牌3 16000点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会小时候就跟贵子一起围著牌桌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不玩了不玩了 不可能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:33.14,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\fsp35\fs150\1c&H3725E9&\t(0,2500,0\fs70)\move(384,4,534,42,33,2619)}麻将帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对手竟然是吟和贵子的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三宅在这吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她朋友发了封电邮到基地来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.74,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H67625F&\pos(228,256)}Re：关于转播的日程表
