Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没寄到基地这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明说好每天发邮件的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要用吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:09.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\fs90\1c&H836B65&\rnd5\be2\frz12.76\frx2\fry6\move(82,346,-610,512,0,2998)}【致三宅日向】羽生第三高中田径队全体
