Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.21,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs80\1c&H48404A&\b0\be1\t(0,1740,0\fs45)\move(114,482,330,448,36,1704)}对不起三宅同学 让你这麽孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是寄给日向的邮件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就这样擅自打开来看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为…因为我很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你一个人不知道在生什麽气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是却什麽都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好把话说清楚啊 不然我会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怕你是不是隐瞒了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怕你是不是有什麽话说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:14.09,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs60\1vc(&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&,&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&)\b0\be2\rnd5\frz341.6\frx28\fry344\pos(392.666,476.667)}对不起三宅同学 让你这麽孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑话说在前头 这可不是什麽好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本来不想提 你们听了也不会好受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}够了 快点说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}简单来说 就是我退出社团的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然是大会 绝对是让跑得快的上场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟什麽年级的无关啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是高三的学姐这次大赛后就要引退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这种原因放水 才是对她们不敬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}200公尺 三宅日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们没跟那个笨蛋说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说了啊 都叫她看看脸色了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那一瞬间 我觉得什麽都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎麽可能 明明都是她们的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们就是明白这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才想尽办法把错推到我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我退队 还乱传我的閒话和谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道这就是你退学的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉我就是条丧家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那发信过来的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 那时候的队友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说想在转播时跟我说几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们说朋友能去南极 自己也很骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才想到「呵呵 我们原来是朋友啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽？和你们的想像有出入？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉这裡都不像是地球了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎？啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好神奇的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们去对面搭帐篷和设置天线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要纠结到什麽时候啊 快忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这样害我都觉得不舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得我为什麽要来南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这裡一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和无拘无束的人们去一无所有的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们看 景色这麽漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冰 地层 雪水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一个都是不曾看过的颜色和形状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有任何我们知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡有著和以往完全不一样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是为了享受这一切才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们这样不就浪费了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 那就把它忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先去扎营 扎营
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是在玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才没有浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定不会浪费这一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟科幻电影一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要喝点水看看 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}某种意义上而言 可能是全世界最乾淨的水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几乎没有被人触碰过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}气温也没有高到能让细菌繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶 冰冰凉凉的好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滋润身心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑要喝看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}联繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说句话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡是伦湾角的小渊泽 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 这裡是昭和 信号良好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}景色如何 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 感觉像是被蛋糕包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子也说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抵达的那一刻喊说「想吃巧克力蛋糕！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈也……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最棒的天然水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理很擅长些怪工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一点也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能从卫星上看到这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 这是给拍卫星照等特殊情况定位用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会非常清晰的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在没在拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿优
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿优
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.33,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.11,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用管她 她每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种地方都有标记 肯定有人在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可没话中有话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是极乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为温度越来越低了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有更厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下一锅水滚了 就做煎蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的很喜欢煎蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在新加坡吃早餐时 也吃了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去打水 你陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不够用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 是我用掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}风吹起来真的超冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我也会有点想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果跟日向有同样的遭遇会怎麽想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:31.50,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs60\1vc(&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&,&HEFCABA&,&H60513F&)\b0\be2\rnd5\frz341.6\frx28\fry344\pos(392.666,476.667)}对不起三宅同学 让你这麽孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遭遇了这麽过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但某天 又若无其事地联络自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为她们所犯下无可挽回的错而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不可能保持平静 不可能笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑又不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把手套捡起来 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑老管閒事真是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 我可能还是挺害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说了 只要手就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你带我一起来这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煎蛋做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\pos(904,84)\frz344.9\frx348\fry16}可选的过年荞麦麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\frx348\fry16\pos(908,202)\frz349.1}加天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H778285&\frx348\fry16\pos(928,296)\frz353.3}加年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H585A5A&\frx348\fry16\frz353.3\pos(912,368)}纯荞麦麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切得真烂 这是刀削麵啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}够细了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重杆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从杆麵开始啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}10分钟后就正式来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果晒痕还是没消
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这说明你在南极玩得很海呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是原谅她们 会轻鬆些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果原谅了能轻鬆点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但想像道完歉 她们鬆了一口气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就一肚子火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「真他妈的」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的肚量也够小的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡是上午9点 和日本有6个小时的时差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正式开始前 我能说一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 你们能别缠著三宅日向了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因为你们 日向才退学 饱受艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们可能觉得她恨你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:06.70,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}深夜零时の地平线　广がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今日がずっ之眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:21.74,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}鼻の奥がツン之した　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:26.27,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:35.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:46.71,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意味なんかないって言われ続けた之しても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:59.29,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空见上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:03.15,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:11.73,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}さあ　迷いなんて置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:18.15,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探しに行くんだ　见果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:26.22,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}勇気出して　进んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:06.70,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}眼前是深夜零点的地平线 一片广大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今天一直是那麽耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:21.74,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我激动得鼻尖一痒 眼前的景象是那麽美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:26.27,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}灿烂到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:35.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}许许多多的人 装满双手也挤不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:46.71,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}都在劝我不要白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:59.29,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只是仰头看见那颠倒的星空 洒下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:03.15,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我会从这裡扬帆启航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:11.73,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}把心裡的迷茫留在岸边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:18.15,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去探索广阔无垠 斑斓神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:26.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要拿出勇气 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能觉得她每天会想起田径队而掉眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向现在和我们过得极其开心而充实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}享受著你们留在日本绝对体验不到的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向已经积极地迈出了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我们一同迈开了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多棒啊 这才是友情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟日向不一样 个性很差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们就怀著这份不安的心情活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们伤害别人 带给别人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就背负著过错活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是伤人的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是伤害我朋友的代价！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如今还想求个心安？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年很快就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有电视看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然是去年的录影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿优！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿优 阿优！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们也来撞掉烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全都撞掉吧 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说不定会撞坏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个铁桶而已 无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那第一下四个人一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2！
Comment: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:23.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}长いトンネ儿の出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:34.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}间违っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:51.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:23:02.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}污れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:13.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言叶も　きっ之见つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:19.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって构わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:23.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}寻找著漫长隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:34.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光气味的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走错了 也别忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:51.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}从这裡开始 我将踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:23:02.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}紧紧捏住手心裡 葬葬的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:13.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}没说出口的话 我也一定会找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:19.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}随你们嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 迈出脚步
